This package installs support files for <b>EPM</b>, the Enhanced Editor
of OS/2 or eComStation. It comes with countless <b>features</b> and <b>bug
fixes</b> for both programmers and standard users, e.g.:

<ul>
<li>user-friendly default configuration
<li>improved keyword highlighting
<li>configurable color schemes and info bars
<li>new menu, toolbar and additional keyset
<li>mode-dependent configuration including syntax expansion with
coding styles and expression matching
<li>improved command shell features
<li>easier configuration to avoid macro recompilation.
</ul>
<br>
